headline: BofA Sees Steady Earnings Momentum Building at J.M. Smucker (SJM)
summary: The J. M. Smucker Company (NYSE:SJM) is included among the 15 Best Blue-Chip Stocks with Growing Dividends. On November 26, BofA lifted its price target on The J. M. Smucker Company (NYSE:SJM) to $120 from $118 while maintaining a Neutral rating. The update followed the company’s Q2 results, where adjusted EPS edged past BofA’s expectations. In […]
